title: Upsets and Undefeated Streaks
description:
Tony Kornheiser and Michael Wilbon discuss if the Dolphins or the Eagles have the more impressive 3-0 start to the season, whose upset was more surprising: the Colts or the Jaguars and if the Packers won the game or the Bucs lost it.
